.         Program Variables and Constants
.
CURRDATE  DIM       8
DESC20    DIM       20
DESC27    DIM       27
DESC30    DIM       30
DIM3A     DIM       3
DIM6      DIM       6
KDATE     DIM       8
KIHOSPID  DIM       3
KIHSNAME  DIM       35
IBCNMHOS  FORM      1
NUMPATS   FORM      3
